<div class="homepage">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="single-service">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <div class="fa fa-home icon-service"></div>
            </h2>
            <h4 class="section-desc">Find Your Home</h4>

            <p>Explain to us exactly what you are looking for and we will do our best to find that ideal property that meets your needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="single-service">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <div class="fa fa-money icon-service"></div>
            </h2>
            <h4 class="section-desc">Sell Your Property</h4>

            <p>If you need to sell your property, get in touch with us. With our experience in the industry and the local area we will get it done in the quickest and simplest way.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="single-service">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <div class="fa fa-user icon-service"></div>
            </h2>
            <h4 class="section-desc">Professional Estate Agents</h4>

            <p>We are professional estate agents. We will help you with all the paperwork and save you money along the way.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="fullwidth-block">
    <div class="container">
      <header data-bg-color="#083461">
        <h2>Top Featured Properties</h2>
      </header>

      <div class="posts-list">
        <div class="row">
          <% @featured_props.each do |featured_property| %>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="fp-block property white list">
                <%= link_to property_path(featured_property) do %>
                  <div class="figure">
                    <%= image_tag featured_property.avatar_url, class: "img-responsive" %>
                  </div>
                <% end %>
                <div class="fp-block-body">
                  <h2 class="title overflow-elip">
                    <%= link_to featured_property.name, property_path(featured_property) %>
                  </h2>
                  <h2 class="subtitle">
                    <div>
                      <span class="precio negrita">
                        Rs. <%= featured_property.price %>
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="fp-block-footer">
                  <ul class="aux-info">
                    <li class="hidden-xs">
                      <i class="fa fa-bed"></i>
                      <small>
                        <%= featured_property.bed_count %>
                      </small>
                    </li>
                    <li class="hidden-xs">
                      <i class="fa fa-shower"></i>
                      <small>
                        <%= featured_property.bath_count %>
                      </small>
                    </li>
                    <li class="hidden-xs">
                      <i class="fa fa-arrows-alt"></i>
                      <small>
                        <%= featured_property.plot_area %><sup>2</sup>
                      </small>
                    </li>
                    <li class="hidden-xs">
                      <i class="fa fa-car"></i>
                      <small>
                        <%= featured_property.garage_count %>
                      </small>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center">
        <a href="house.html" class="button">See more houses</a>
      </p>
    </div> <!-- .container -->
  </div> <!-- .fullwidth-block -->

  <div class="fullwidth-block">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="post-grid">
        <div class="post">
          <figure class="featured-image">
            <%= image_tag "dummy/large-thumb-1" %>
          </figure>
          <div class="post-detail">
            <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="house.html">Donec bibendum est lobortis molestie auctor lorem</a></h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Sunt temporibus voluptates id praesentium nihil. Aspernatur, quo. Est laboriosam consectetur atque quo eius. Libero excepturi quam dolorum quia sapiente, saepe velit!</p>
            <span class="arrow"></span>
          </div> <!-- .post-detail -->
        </div> <!-- .post -->
        <div class="post">
          <figure class="featured-image">
            <%= image_tag "dummy/large-thumb-1" %>
          </figure>
          <div class="post-detail">
            <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="house.html">Donec bibendum est lobortis molestie auctor lorem</a></h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Sunt temporibus voluptates id praesentium nihil. Aspernatur, quo. Est laboriosam consectetur atque quo eius. Libero excepturi quam dolorum quia sapiente, saepe velit!</p>
            <span class="arrow"></span>
